sup></mrow></mfrac></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced close=\"]\" open=\"[\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">S</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>-</mo></mrow></msup></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">K</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></msub><mo>&#215;</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mstyle><mo>&#215;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>13</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&#215;</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mstyle><mo>&#215;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&#160;</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">M</mi></math><br />&nbsp;</p>","type":"mcq","source":"JEE Main 2018 (08 Apr)","image":null},{"id":28031,"subject":"Chemistry","chapter":"Chemical Equilibrium","question":"","options":["1.8 atm","0.3 atm","3 atm","0.18 atm"],"answer":0,"solution":"$\\begin{array}{lc}\\mathrm{CO}_2(\\mathrm{~g})+\\mathrm{C}(\\mathrm{s}) \\rightleftharpoons & 2 \\mathrm{CO}(\\mathrm{g}) \\\\ 0.5 & - \\\\ 0.5-\\mathrm{x} & 2 \\mathrm{x}\\end{array}$\n\n\n$\\begin{aligned}\\mathrm{P}_{\\text {total }}=0.5+\\mathrm{x}=0.8 \\\\  \\mathrm{x}=0.3 \\\\  \\mathrm{~K}_{\\mathrm{P}}=\\frac{(0.6)^2}{0.2}=1.8\\end{aligned}$","type":"mcq","source":"JEE Main 2025 (22 Jan Shift 1)","image":null}]